    public class FamilyPicker
extends KSJInternalFrame
    The FamilyPicker is a window that displays a menu of Family objects. When one family is selected, its fields are displayed to confirm it is the right one. When the User clicks the "Choose" button, the Family selected is added to the appropriate field(s) of the editor which launched this picker.

    It is an extension of KSJInternalFrame so it will appear in the View menu.
